OL,3,COver 170 arrested in gig economy
OL,4,Ccrackdown as delivery drivers face
OL,5,Cdeportation
OL,7,FThose arrested included Chinese
OL,8,Fnationals working in a restaurant in
OL,9,FSolihull, West Midlands, Bangladeshi
OL,10,Fand Indian riders in Newham, east
OL,11,FLondon, and Indian delivery riders in
OL,12,FNorwich, Norfolk.
OL,14,FVideo footage released by the Home
OL,15,FOffice of wider action shows officers
OL,16,Fescorting an arrested man into the
OL,17,Fback of an immigration enforcement
OL,18,Fvan, arresting another man by his bike
OL,19,Fin the street, and Home Secretary
OL,20,FShabana Mahmood present at an
OL,21,Foperation in Streatham, south London.
