OL,7,FThe law enforcement drive, which saw
OL,8,F60 people detained for removal from
OL,9,Fthe UK, comes as ministers crack down
OL,10,Fon illegal working, as part of ongoing
OL,11,Fefforts to deter those coming to the
OL,12,Fcountry illegally.
OL,14,FHome Office figures show there were
OL,15,F8,232 arrests of illegal workers in
OL,16,Fthe year to September, up 63% on 5,043
OL,17,Fin the previous 12 months.
