OL,7,FMinisters have also been working with
OL,8,Ffirms Deliveroo, Just Eat and Uber
OL,9,FEats to address concerns of abuse in
OL,10,Fthe sector and ramping up identity
OL,11,Fchecks to tackle account-sharing.
OL,13,FThe Home Office also agreed in July to
OL,14,Fshare asylum hotel locations with food
OL,15,Fdelivery companies, to tackle
OL,16,Fsuspected hot spots of illegal working.
