OL,7,FMahmood set out a raft of reforms to
OL,8,Fthe asylum system last month, aimed at
OL,9,Fmaking the UK less attractive for
OL,10,Fillegal migration and making it easier
OL,11,Fto deport people.
OL,13,FBorder security minister Alex Norris
OL,14,Fsaid: "These results should send a
OL,15,Fclear message, if you are working
OL,16,Fillegally in this country, you will be
OL,17,Farrested and removed.
