OL,7,F"As well as delivering record levels
OL,8,Fof enforcement, we are tightening the
OL,9,Flaw to clamp down on illegal working
OL,10,Fin the delivery sector to root out
OL,11,Fthis criminality from our communities.
OL,13,F"This action is part of the most
OL,14,Fsweeping changes to illegal migration
OL,15,Fin modern times to reduce the
OL,16,Fincentives that draw illegal
OL,17,Fmigrations here and scale up removals."
